\Phi_{0}\left(\kappa^{a}_{0},\theta_{0}\right) & =V^{\top}_{0,1}\phi_{0,1}\left(V^{\top}_{0,0}\kappa^{a}_{0}\right)\\
 & =V^{\top}_{0,1}\phi_{0,1}\left(\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
-0.9 & -0.8 & -0.7 & -0.6\\
-0.5 & -0.4 & -0.3 & -0.2
