\end_inset

We have
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Phi_{2}\left(\psi_{2}\left(\kappa_{2}\right),\theta_{2}\right) & =V^{\top}_{2,1}\phi_{2,1}\left(V^{\top}_{2,0}\psi_{2}\left(\kappa_{2}\right)\right)\\
 & =V^{\top}_{2,1}\phi_{2,1}\left(\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
