status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
While adaptive RISE techniques like 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Bidikli.Tatlicioglu.ea2014a"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 could be used to compensate for unknown bounds 
\begin_inset Formula $\overline{d},\overline{\dot{d}},\overline{\ddot{d}}$
\end_inset

,
 the described formulation therein yields asymptotic convergence of the tracking error.
 Achieving exponential convergence without Assumption 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "asm:d-bounds"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

 remains an open challenge.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

