 & +\left(k_{1}+k_{2}\right)r_{2}\left(t\right)-\left(k_{1}k_{2}+k^{2}_{2}+k^{2}_{1}\right)r_{1}\left(t\right)+k^{3}_{1}e\left(t\right),
\end{alignedat}
