q^{\top} & \dot{q}^{\top}\end{array}\right]^{\top}\in\overline{B}_{\overline{q}_{\text{d}}+\overline{\dot{q}}_{\text{d}}+s}\left(0_{2n}\right)}\left(\left\Vert \left.\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial\dot{q}^{2}}\right|_{\left(q,\dot{q}\right)}\right\Vert +\left\Vert \left.\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial\dot{q}\partial q}\right|_{\left(q,\dot{q}\right)}\right\Vert \right)
