\begin_inset Formula $V\left(z_{P}\left(t\right)\right)\geq0$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $t\in\mathcal{T}$
\end_inset

.
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $z_{P}$
\end_inset

