\begin_inset Formula $\dot{V}\left(t\right)\triangleq\frac{{\rm d}}{{\rm d}t}V\left(z_{P}\left(t\right)\right)=\left(\nabla V\left(z_{P}\left(t\right)\right)\right)^{\top}\dot{z}_{P}\left(t\right)$
\end_inset

 for almost all 
\begin_inset Formula $t\in\mathcal{T}$
\end_inset

,
