\begin_inset Formula $\nabla V\left(z_{P}\right)=\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
e^{\top} & r^{\top}_{1} & r^{\top}_{2} & 1\end{array}\right]^{\top}.$
\end_inset

 The derivative of (
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:lyapunov"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset

